{"tid":51111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李克強：中央政府對梁振英及特區政府工作充分肯定","createTime":"2016-12-23T03:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T03:09:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4afcb86190b132b34a937da62ff945d8b0a166d1","tid":51111,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"在北京述職的行政長官梁振英，上午獲國務院總理李克強接見。<br />\n<br />\n李克強表示，中央政府充分肯定梁振英和特區政府的工作，中央政府會繼續堅持一國兩制、港人治港、高度自治方針，嚴格按照憲法和基本法辦事。李克強又讚揚梁振英積極進取，務實有為，繼續發展經濟，改善民生。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，中央會繼續出台有利於香港的政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1303877-20161223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1303877-20161223.htm&d=NVi04CGZMQiyBxT8TxLyVpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4be106fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1303877-20161223.htm&h=c1c02059\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1303877-20161223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"731d4c124e3e305baebca1b986dbf2ec1e285f0d","tid":51111,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8072d38a26d164d8681b0dd707010bde3ffa34e2","tid":51111,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T03:09:22.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}